keytool used for key management , certificate. (creation , modification , deletion).
store & protect keys (private keys , public keys , secret keys) & certificate using keystore.
keystore a db file , that keytool uses , to store keys certificates.
trustStore store all trusted CA certificates. they never contain private key or secret key.
   -rule certificate from trusted certificate authority such as  digicert , entrust 

  
